Description: # Offset
        ### What is this?
        To encode & decode by shift text.
        
        ### How to install?
        ```bash
        pip install Offset
        ```
        
        ## - How to use
        
        - import as a module
        
        ```python
        from offset import Offset
        Offset.convert(text, number)
        ```
        
        - Command mode:
        
        ```bash
        offset -n 10 -s 'Hello'
        ```
        
        - File mode:
        >The new file will be stored at '~/offset_export/filename_%Y%m%d_%H%M%S.ext'
        
        ```bash
        offset -n 10 -f '/filepath/and/filename.ext'
        ```
        
        - Interactive mode
        
        ```bash
        offset -i [-n int]
        ```
        
